PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT that will amend the definitions of "watercourse" and "inter-provincial lakes" set forth in the MASTER AGREEMENT administered by the PRAIRIE PROVINCES WATER BOARD, as well as replace the references to the Exchequer Court of Canada with references to the Federal Court of Canada, and re-define "apportionment period".
